title: Star Wars Rebel Assault II: The Hidden Empire
description:
Rebel Assault II: The Hidden Empire


REBEL2_A.iso = CD1
REBEL2_B.iso = CD2

I've given the cd's their original cd names for bringing more pleasure into it xD
Unstripped and untouched <3

Play it from the cd-image or copy the files from both images to a directory of your choice. Either way it saves the game progress on your computer at C:/REBEL2/

I've played this on Windows XP without any problems, i hope you do to!


Saw this one laying around so i decided to put it up here, hope you enjoy it!
Maybe i'll post more retro games if i find any in my shelves!


PS: This is my first upload EVER so be nice ^^
